        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p><hr /><p>You can transform your body into a gaseous vapor. In this state, you're amorphous. You lose any item bonus to AC and all other effects and bonuses from armor, and you use your proficiency rank in unarmored defense. You gain resistance 8 to physical damage and are immune to precision damage. You can't cast spells, activate items, or use actions that have the attack or manipulate trait. You gain a fly Speed equal to your normal fly Speed and can slip through tiny cracks. This form lasts for 5 minutes or until you Dismiss it.</p>"
